Gets details about a bill including outstanding balance, due date, status, and payment history.

### HTTP Request

`POST <%= config.host %>/bill/detail`

### Post Parameters

Param | Description
----- | -----------
`userId` | Unbill user ID.
`companyId` | Unbill company ID.

### 200 Response Body

Attribute | Description
--------- | -----------
`bill` | Bill object
`company` | Company object
`payments` | List of past bill payments
`payments.amount` | Amount paid
`payments.paidOn` | Date of payment